ov 11006873 A Vision for the Future of Genomics Research The primary focus of this document was a plan for translating genomic research into health applications Without protections in place like those outlined in S 1053 this vision may not be realized because of the public s fear of taking advantage of these advances Today at the dawn of the genomic era is the ideal time to pass this legislation and get it onto the President s desk for his signature http www whitehouse gov omb legislative sap 108 1 s1053sap s pdf White House Office of Mangement and Budget OMB Statement privacy cfm Privacy 10002900 Contact accessibility cfm Accessibility sitemap cfm Site Index staffSearch cfm Staff Search Home Government Links http www os dhhs gov H H S logo link to U S Department of Health and Human Services DHHS http www firstgov gov FirstGov FirstGov http www nih gov NIH NIH
